article_id:82,category_name:News,title_name:Update Concerning an Issue with Purchases [Addendum],image_path:,message:<div>We are aware that some players are experiencing issues with in-game purchases.</div><div><br></div><div>We are currently working with the platform holder to fix this, and expect to see some improvements in the upcoming November update.</div><div><br></div><div>Another notification will be sent out once the fix has been applied.</div><div><br></div><div><span style="color: rgb(41, 105, 176);"><strong>Addendum (<span class="local_date" data-local_date="1542198000"></span>)</strong></span><br><br>The issue with in-game purchases has been fixed in version 1.1.5.<br>Thank you for your patience.<br><br>Please follow the procedure below if you have experienced any in-game purchase issues:<br>1. Tap Complete Purchases at the bottom of the Diamantium purchase screen or at the bottom of the Value Packs purchase screen.<br>Tap Close when the message below appears:<br>&quot;The purchase process has been reinitiated. If an incomplete purchase currently exists, that purchase will now be completed.&quot;<br>2. Close and restart the game. Diamantium and Value Packs can now be purchased normally.<br><br>Once again, we thank you for your patience while this issue was getting resolved.<br><br>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1541655600,update_time1542198044